test_list_of_single_number:
assert [] == [[46]]
  Right contains one more item: [46]
  Full diff:
  - [[46]]
  + []
test_list_of_several_same_number:
assert [] == [[46], [46], [46]]
  Right contains 3 more items, first extra item: [46]
  Full diff:
  - [[46], [46], [46]]
  + []
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 2116 == 46
 +  where 2116 = <built-in function prod>([1, 2, 23, 46])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
